    {
      "id": "1009765",
      "title": "",
      "description": "Pedestrian Access:\r\nThere will be no access between the Hingham Ferry Terminal and DCR building. Pedestrian access to the and from the ferry dock will be through and around the west side of the Hingham Ferry Terminal. Some sidewalk access at the Terminal may also be restricted during this work.\r\n\r\nShipyard Drive:\r\nShipyard Drive will be closed to traffic in front of the Hingham Ferry Terminal starting at 9 AM on Wednesday, May 20. Traffic will be rerouted through the Hingham Parking lot. Drop-offs and pick-ups will be relocated to the parking lot. Traffic police and signage will be in place to direct traffic. This closure should last approximately one week. ",
